            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I was student of this school form 5 Years. In 5 years, I suffered from many horrible experience in this School. Always full class used to be ready for blaming me. I had stammering problem, many children used to trouble by acting like me. Children used to trouble me / beat false accusation on me. So many times, I used to be punished even when it is not my mistake. Also many times teachers had also insulted me front of whole class, by telling; 'Nobody will talk to him or be his friend' & ‘You will be removed from the School’. I was repeated in class 6, so teachers had insulted me; 'we will repeat you again in this class'. Even some parents had scolded me for no reason. I know some of the teachers who never ever behaved nice with me in 5 Years. Form all this trouble; my mother had to plan to leave the school. Therefore, I left the school in middle of the year.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
